OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774667002
OL,3,CPregnant women and cancer patients 'at
OL,4,Crisk' because of sonographer shortage
OL,6,FPregnant women and cancer patients
OL,7,Fcould face "life-threatening" delays
OL,8,Fbecause of a growing shortage of
OL,9,Fsonographers, experts have warned.
OL,11,FThe Society of Radiographers (SoR)
OL,12,Fsaid the vacancy rate for sonographers
OL,13,Fis 24.2% across England, rising to
OL,14,F38.2% in some areas.
OL,16,FThe census also showed that about one
OL,17,Fin every 13 (7.6%) sonographers are
OL,18,Fplanning to retire within the next
OL,19,Fyear.
OL,26,@oD@LOUoD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
