OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774667002
OL,3,CPregnant women and cancer patients 'at
OL,4,Crisk' because of sonographer shortage
OL,6,FSonographers conduct ultrasound scans
OL,7,Fwhich are essential to pregnancy care
OL,8,Fand are also used in the diagnosis of
OL,9,Fcancer.
OL,11,FPregnant women are offered a scan when
OL,12,Ftheir baby is 12 weeks old and again
OL,13,Fwhen the baby is 20 weeks.
OL,15,F"Hospitals try their very best to get
OL,16,Fthe three-month and five-month
OL,17,Fantenatal screening scans done on
OL,18,Ftime," said Katie Thompson, SoR
OL,19,Fpresident and a practising sonographer.
OL,26,@wD@AOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774667002
OL,3,CPregnant women and cancer patients 'at
OL,4,Crisk' because of sonographer shortage
OL,6,F"But when there aren't enough staff,
OL,7,Fprioritising those scans has a knock-
OL,8,Fon effect on more urgent later foetal
OL,9,Fgrowth scans, which in some cases need
OL,10,Fto be done within 24 or 36 hours.
OL,12,F"Departments end up struggling to fit
OL,13,Fin patients who need these emergency
OL,14,Fscans.
OL,16,F"Sometimes hospitals pull in
OL,17,Fsonographers from other areas to keep
OL,18,Fthe antenatal services going. But then
OL,19,Fthat's at the expense of those other
OL,20,Fservices."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774667002
OL,3,CPregnant women and cancer patients 'at
OL,4,Crisk' because of sonographer shortage
OL,6,FOn scans for cancer diagnosis she
OL,7,Fadded: "When a person is feeling
OL,8,Funwell, their first investigation is
OL,9,Foften an ultrasound scan.
OL,11,F"And then follow-up care after cancer
OL,12,Ftreatment often takes the form of
OL,13,Fregular ultrasound scans.
OL,15,F"The Government's recent cancer plan
OL,16,Fspoke about increasing testing and
OL,17,Freducing waiting lists.
OL,19,F"But sonography is one of the
OL,20,Fbeginning points for people being
OL,21,Fdiagnosed with cancer.
OL,26,@oD@HOUsD@AOUwD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774667002
OL,3,CPregnant women and cancer patients 'at
OL,4,Crisk' because of sonographer shortage
OL,6,F"With the current workforce shortfall,
OL,7,Fit's going to be very, very hard to
OL,8,Fdecrease waiting times.
OL,10,F"And if cancers aren't picked up when
OL,11,Fthey should be, that can have an
OL,12,Feffect on the patient's outcome."
OL,14,FThe new SoR census showed that the
OL,15,Fhighest vacancy rates for sonographers
OL,16,Fwere in the south east of England,
OL,17,Fwhere almost two in five posts are
OL,18,Fvacant (38.2%).
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUtD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774667002
OL,3,CPregnant women and cancer patients 'at
OL,4,Crisk' because of sonographer shortage
OL,6,FThere is also a 34.6% shortfall in
OL,7,FLondon and three in 10 (30%) posts in
OL,8,Fthe North West are vacant.
OL,10,FBut in the North East and Yorkshire
OL,11,Fthere is a shortfall of 11%, the SoR
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FMs Thompson added: "Training new
OL,15,Fsonographers takes quite a while, so
OL,16,Fincreasing numbers can't be done very
OL,17,Fquickly.
OL,26,@vD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774667002
OL,3,CPregnant women and cancer patients 'at
OL,4,Crisk' because of sonographer shortage
OL,6,F"The fact that numbers are dropping
OL,7,Fshows that the number of sonographers
OL,8,Fbeing trained isn't keeping up with
OL,9,Fdemand and hasn't kept up for a long
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,F"We're still waiting for the
OL,13,FGovernment to publish its NHS
OL,14,Fworkforce plan. They've put out their
OL,15,Fcancer plan but the workforce plan
OL,16,Fshould be integral to that.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774667002
OL,3,CPregnant women and cancer patients 'at
OL,4,Crisk' because of sonographer shortage
OL,6,F"You can't say that you're going to
OL,7,Finvest in all these new scanners and
OL,8,Fopen all these community diagnostic
OL,9,Fcentres unless you've thought about
OL,10,Fthe professionals who are going to
OL,11,Fconduct the scans and provide patient
OL,12,Fcare."
OL,14,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,15,Fspokesperson said: "We recognise the
OL,16,Fpressures facing diagnostic services,
OL,17,Fincluding the sonography workforce,
OL,18,Fand we are taking action to ensure the
OL,19,FNHS has the skilled staff it needs to
OL,20,Fmeet rising demand and deliver timely
OL,21,Fcare to patients.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@FO]wD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774667002
OL,3,CPregnant women and cancer patients 'at
OL,4,Crisk' because of sonographer shortage
OL,6,F"We have already taken action to
OL,7,Fexpand services for patients, rolling
OL,8,Fout new community diagnostic centres
OL,9,Fand expanding opening hours, keeping
OL,10,Fpatients away from busy hospitals and
OL,11,Fcared for in their local communities."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
